Also please call me Mochi-Chan!!^^

summary: Hello I would like to request a match up I'm 5'5 with chocolate brown skin my hair is sapphire blue and black (as of right now)...
question: Hello I would like to request a match up I'm 5'5 with chocolate brown skin my hair is sapphire blue and black (as of right now) I wear big glasses I'm a Pisces I work out to get stronger I'm not very sensitive and a bit cold but if I know you I well I'm supportive and am willing to do anything for you I usually wear long sweater dresses that go up to my knees and boots that go to the middle of my calf and black leggings and I usually wear my hair up I like having fun and music(happy Valentine's)
answer:
Happy belated Valentines! XDD

~~~

I match you up with….Jirou Kyouka!

She respects how you work hard to refine your skills and better yourself, and expresses her support in subtle , casual ways, willing to help you in any way when you need it. She is a pretty independent individual, and thus does not require you to constantly show affection and love, knowing that although you may seem slightly distant at times, you certainly care about her, and your relationship is very relaxed and natural, with both of you knowing each other’s feelings undoubtedly without having to prove to one another.

Although your styles are quite different, she is intrigued by your fashion and you regularly take her out shopping, introducing her to new genres and encouraging her to try them out. She, being an avid fan of music, does the same for you in that area, showing you the best songs she thinks you’d like, and you two are frequently seen walking together sharing a pair of earphones.

I hope you like your result!

body:
Headcanon time!

So… first of all I’m probably overthinking this/misinterpreting it… and I don’t really have anything to back my theory up…

But!

I think Shiragumo might be Kurogiri!

I mean…

  • We have no clue who Kurogiri is right?
  • He is a subordinate of AfO… means he can have gotten the warp gate quirk from him…
  • The name… kuro/shira… (if I’m correct) are black/white… (and come on! Is that coincidence? In a manga? O.o)
  • This would actually explain some things without a teacher/student being a traitor I think
  • Because Shiragumo was at UA! He knows where to look for infos there!
  • And! If he is the same age as Aizawa and Mic… he probably knows the Pussycats too…
  • He would be the same age as A LOT of pros we know
  • (On the other hand… it turning out like this… would be a hit in the gut for Aizawa and the others… it will be painful! And heartbreaking …)
  • (Because he is probably declared dead or vanished or something…)
